  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Alpenrose is chalet style hotel recently constructed in local stone and wood offering quality, contemporary accommodation in spacious suites. </p>
<p>Offering dinners in its gastronomic restaurant, you can enjoy apartment-style living with meals provided. Located in the Bergers area, access to the skiing couldn't be easier and the views across the mountains are some of the best in the Alps.</p>
<p>Take advantage of the outdoor heated pool and steam room after a hard days skiing or treat yourself to a relaxing massage (pay locally).</p>]]></description>
